{"tid":243032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死6隻]清理豬舍化糞池 一家6口相繼沼氣中毒死亡","createTime":"2017-05-14T11:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T11:18:00.000Z","uid":32407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c8deb6c1976545c9e6ab211903321ac121f57f","tid":243032,"uid":32407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2066922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2066922&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiujOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=06b9814c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2066922&h=d8f7c4ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2066922</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國廣東省發生一起沼氣中毒死亡意外，有外媒報導指出，廣東潮州市的王小姐昨天清理自家豬舍化糞池時，卻因沼氣中毒昏迷在化糞池內，她的父母、兄弟、親友相繼下去搶救，全部也昏迷在內，最後醫護人員搶救無效，事故造成一共6人死亡。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，該起意外發生在潮州饒平縣南山村，昨天上午村民王先生一家到自家豬舍化糞池，打算抽取化糞池水澆在果園，但因為管道堵塞，王先生的女兒下去化糞池處理堵塞，但卻昏迷在內，王先生夫婦和2名兒子發現後相繼下去搶救，卻全部陷入昏迷。之後王先生另外一名兒子打電話向父親好友呂先生求救，呂先生也昏迷在化糞池內。<br />\n6人全部陷入昏迷後，當地相關單位緊急趕赴現場救人，搶救過後，仍然宣告6名昏迷者死亡，當地政府於13日晚間也派員慰問意外事件的死者家屬且送達慰問金。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891861dd50d0bbcb0a4d1dc0ac283907060e8358","tid":243032,"uid":19497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"想像到個畫面覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd77ab487d4d33d